title: Judge rejects Google claim that DOJ’s Jonathan Kanter is improperly biased
description: A federal judge rejected Google’s claims that one of the architects behind a Department of Justice case, Assistant Attorney General Jonathan Kanter, should submit to the company’s questioning at a deposition.

title: Your iPhone 15 could be free. It might still be a bad deal.
description: AT&T, T-Mobile and Verizon offer free or discounted new iPhone 15 models when you trade in old devices. We ran the math on “free” iPhones for two households.

title: TikTok and U.S. rekindle negotiations, boosting app’s hopes for survival
description: Calls to ban the wildly popular app have faded ahead of the 2024 election.

title: The abortion bot will see you now
description: An abortion bot from abortion access organizations including Planned Parenthood is rolling out — even in states with abortion bans — to help people find care.
